Organization: Northwestern University, Evanston Illinois.
Lines: 545

Hi everyone!

This is Game 4.  It's dedicated to *dfs 6d*, who gave me the first
impression how a real strong player plays.  True, I had some Go books
containing some pro game records (which are supposedly better), but to see
it really happening, to see it move by move (LIVE :), i first experienced
it when watching a dfs game on IGS.

Of course, dfs is not a pro and he doesn't play pro game either.  But had
he been a pro, i wonder if i ever had the chance to make him a friend. :-)

jzy NR ^_^

