White[ib]
Comment[B's group doesn't have complete eyeshape, so B will have to escape.  On the other hand, W's top group is as solid as a rock, and there is no way for B to take advantage of.  \(Shi, playing W, later pointed out that B should have played J18 before E16.  Had he did, B would be in a much better shape.\)]
